channel.title: Mossman vs. Prison Break government employee
channel.description:
Hi!
I just sat and went through some prison break episodes (once again) and when this girl in episode s01e17 starts to talk @ about 08 : 30, I cant help to think that she's the exact same voice as Mossman in half-life 2.
Someone else noticed this? Can someone dig up if it really is her, or do they just sound just alike?
If you can't watch the episode.
[url]https://www.icefilms.info/ip.php?v=6311&[/url]
Icefilms is NOT illegal to use since it's a stream, only the third-part uploaders is help responsible.
Edit: I found it. [url]https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michelle_Forbes[/url]
